window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Teacher by day, stalker by night.</b></p> <p>Who ever thought college could be this interesting?</p> <p>I'm teaching a hundred students. But my eyes are only on one. She's my obsession—and I'll stop at nothing to make her mine.</p> <p>I followed her back to her apartment. Then I broke in while she was asleep.</p> <p>She wants me. I can feel it when I touch her. But she can't know who I am.</p> <p>I'm her new step-brother.</p> <p>My family's enemies are legion, and our little game puts her right in the firing line. But protecting her is what big brothers are for, right?</p> <p>The more we fight, the more I want her. And my nocturnal visits make her want me, too.</p> <p>Am I her guardian angel? Or a devil in disguise?</p>"; 
